<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/47714170-cassie-price"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1472521782i/47714170._UY100_CR16,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
