<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/47714170-cassie-price">Cassie Price</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">My guess is because there is no sex in it.<br/><br/>Without giving anything away, the format of the book also means there isn&apos;t time and space for a lot of extr<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">My guess is because there is no sex in it.<br /><br />Without giving anything away, the format of the book also means there isn't time and space for a lot of extra words. You'll find out why on the first page. <br /><br />But this also means that the characters aren't as developed as many adult novels. <br /><br />I'm 35 and I LOVED it.<br /><br />I also blew up the phones of all my book loving friends insisting they read it. They might say demanded but I digress.<br /><br />Read it. I read it in two days and started it again the very next morning. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
