        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer835891785" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10155214065074325361">i loved this book, don&apos;t get me wrong. it has great characters and is well-researched and detailed and every scene comes alive and pops with tension and it also has all that slippery writing that i really appreciate. but how fans are practically burning effigies of veronica roth for the feels she made them feel or whatever, while this book is Beloved By All is beyond me. this book definitely has more brutal feels.<br/><br/>but—a great book, whose secrets will not be spoilt by me with a more detailed revie</span>
  <span id="freeText10155214065074325361" style="display:none">i loved this book, don't get me wrong. it has great characters and is well-researched and detailed and every scene comes alive and pops with tension and it also has all that slippery writing that i really appreciate. but how fans are practically burning effigies of veronica roth for the feels she made them feel or whatever, while this book is Beloved By All is beyond me. this book definitely has more brutal feels.<br><br>but—a great book, whose secrets will not be spoilt by me with a more detailed review; careless talk costs lives and all...<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1528725630i/25720315.png" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><a href="http://bloggycomelately.com/" rel="nofollow noopener">come to my blog!</a></span>
